 Language":"Search for language","Search from GIF Keyboard":"Search from GIF keyboard","Search, share and upload your own GIFs to your Tenor account and access them anywhere, anytime.":"Search, share and upload your own GIFs to your Tenor account and access them anywhere and at any time.","See GIFs":"See GIFs","See More":"See more","See all":"See all","See all Press":"See all press","Select account":"Select account","Serbian":"Serbian","Serbian (Latin)":"Serbian (Latin)","Serving more than 200 million monthly active users and processing more than 200 million daily search requests, Tenor is the largest and fastest-growing mobile GIF-sharing platform. Our GIF Keyboard app is the most-downloaded in its category on both iOS and Android. And we power GIF-sharing for partners including Apple iMessage, Facebook Messenger, WhatsApp, Google Gboard, Kik, LinkedIn, Touchpal and others.":"Serving more than 200 million monthly active users and processing more than 200 million daily search requests, Tenor is the largest and fastest-growing mobile GIF-sharing platform. Our GIF keyboard app is the most downloaded in its category on both iOS and Android. And we power GIF sharing for partners including Apple iMessage, Facebook Messenger, WhatsApp, Google Gboard, Kik, LinkedIn, Touchpal and others.","Share Anywhere":"Share anywhere","Share Packs":"Share packs","Share URL":"Share URL","Share Your Gif":"Share your GIF","Share anywhere":"Share anywhere","Share from GIF Keyboard":"Share from GIF keyboard","Share to {name}.":"Share to {name}.","Share with millions":"Share with millions","Shares":"Shares","Showtime has found valuable Tenor Insights for its new show {billionsLink} and also had recent success with working with Tenor on resurfacing {dexterLink} content for the 10-year anniversary of the series. In addition to showcasing trending on-air content, tapping into legacy content and assembling a GIF strategy that rekindles consumer excitement is a strong suit of the Tenor Partner Success Team.":"Showtime has found valuable Tenor Insights for its new show {billionsLink} and also had recent success working with Tenor on resurfacing {dexterLink} content for the 10-year anniversary of the series. In addition to showcasing trending on-air content, tapping into legacy content and assembling a GIF strategy that rekindles consumer excitement is a strong suit of the Tenor partner success team.","Sign in with Google":"Sign in with Google","Sinhala":"Sinhala","Slovak":"Slovak","Slovenian":"Slovenian","Social Accounts":"Social accounts","Spanish":"Spanish","Spanish (Argentina)":"Spanish (Argentina)","Spanish (Bolivia)":"Spanish (Bolivia)","Spanish (Chile)":"Spanish (Chile)","Spanish (Colombia)":"Spanish (Colombia)","Spanish (Costa Rica)":"Spanish (Costa Rica)","Spanish (Dominican Republic)":"Spanish (Dominican Republic)","Spanish (Ecuador)":"Spanish (Ecuador)","Spanish (El Salvador)":"Spanish (El Salvador)","Spanish (Guatemala)":"Spanish (Guatemala)","Spanish (Honduras)":"Spanish (Honduras)","Spanish (Latin America)":"Spanish (Latin America)","Spanish (Mexico)":"Spanish (Mexico)","Spanish (Nicaragua)":"Spanish (Nicaragua)","Spanish (Panama)":"Spanish (Panama)","Spanish (Paraguay)":"Spanish (Paraguay)","Spanish (Peru)":"Spanish (Peru)","Spanish (Puerto Rico)":"Spanish (Puerto Rico)","Spanish (United States)":"Spanish (United States)","Spanish (Uruguay)":"Spanish (Uruguay)","Spanish (Venezuela)":"Spanish (Venezuela)","Start Uploading":"Start uploading","Step one: Let’s talk! {contactUsLink} now to get started in fueling fandom with mobile GIF sharing.":"Step one: Let’s talk! {contactUsLink} now to get started in fuelling fandom with mobile GIF sharing.","Stickers":"Stickers","Suggested Language":"Suggested language","Swahili":"Swahili","Swedish":"Swedish","Tag and Discovery":"Tag and Discovery","Tag your GIFs to be discovered & Shared. Search for your content on Tenor’s partners, including Gboard, Twitter, and many more.":"Tag your GIFs to be discovered and shared. Search for your content on Tenor’s partners, including Gboard, Twitter and many more.","Tagalog":"Tagalog","Tamil":"Tamil","Tap and hold your GIF for sharing options":"Tap and hold your GIF for sharing options","Tap the edit icon to trim, crop, and caption.":"Tap the edit icon to trim, crop and caption.","Tap to Upload Here":"Tap to upload here","Telugu":"Telugu","Tenor Apps":"Tenor apps","Tenor Content Partners":"Tenor content partners","Tenor Data Usage":"Tenor data usage","Tenor Emotional Graph":"Tenor emotional graph","Tenor GIF API":"Tenor GIF API","Tenor GIF Keyboard - Bring Personality To Your Conversations":"Tenor GIF keyboard – bring personality to your conversations","Tenor Terms of Service":"Tenor Terms of Service","Tenor drives mobile GIF sharing for top entertainment brands":"Tenor drives mobile GIF sharing for top entertainment brands","Tenor in the Press":"Tenor in the press","Tenor is backed by marquee investors including \u003Cstrong\u003ERedpoint Ventures\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, \u003Cstrong\u003EMenlo Ventures\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, \u003Cstrong\u003ETenaya Capital\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, \u003Cstrong\u003EOCA Ventures\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, \u003Cstrong\u003ESignia Ventures\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, \u003Cstrong\u003ECowboy Ventures\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E and others.":"Tenor is backed by marquee investors including \u003Cstrong\u003ERedpoint Ventures\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, \u003Cstrong\u003EMenlo Ventures\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, \u003Cstrong\u003ETenaya Capital\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, \u003Cstrong\u003EOCA Ventures\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, \u003Cstrong\u003ESignia Ventures\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E, \u003Cstrong\u003ECowboy Ventures\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E and others.","Tenor is everywhere":"Tenor is everywhere","Tenor logo":"Tenor logo","Tenor now accepts JPG and PNG images. Upload and share your favorite Memes!":"Tenor now accepts JPG and PNG images. Upload and share your favourite memes!","Tenor was founded in 2014 by a team of successful entrepreneurs with a vision to define a new visual language for the world's 3+ billion mobile users.":"Tenor was founded in 2014 by a team of successful entrepreneurs with a vision to define a new visual language for the world's 3+ billion mobile users.","Tenor was not granted the necessary permissions.":"Tenor was not granted the necessary permissions.","Tenor.com has been translated based on your browser's language setting. If you want to change the language, click {langLink}.":"Tenor.com has been translated based on your browser's language setting. If you want to change the language, click {langLink}.","Terms & Privacy":"Terms and privacy","Terms and Privacy":"Terms and privacy","Terms of Service":"Terms of Service","Thai":"Thai","The Tenor Advantage":"The Tenor advantage","The Tenor Partner Success team will work closely with you to create and curate GIF content well-suited to driving consumer engagement in mobile messaging. We’ll ingest your content into our system and optimize it for mobile delivery. The {emotionlGraphLink} will map your content to relevant search terms and surface it when our 200+ million users are looking for just the right GIF to communicate their thoughts and feelings with family and friends.":"The Tenor partner success team will work closely with you to create and curate GIF content well suited to driving consumer engagement in mobile messaging. We’ll ingest your content into our system and optimise it for mobile delivery. The {emotionlGraphLink} will map your content to relevant search terms and surface it when our 200+ million users are looking for just the right GIF to communicate their thoughts and feelings with family and friends.","The best experience is in the app!":"The best experience is in the app!","The challenge of {netflixLink} tune-in is clearly different from linear television. GIFs for Netflix shows tend to trend in the weeks building up to release, so Netflix has teamed with Tenor to drive social momentum using GIFs, creating sustained tune-in for its shows {narcosLink}, {dearwhitepeopleLink}, {masterofnoneLink}, {thecrownLink}, and the upcoming Will Smith feature film, {brightLink}.":"The challenge of {netflixLink} tune-in is clearly different from linear television. GIFs for Netflix shows tend to trend in the weeks building up to release, so Netflix has teamed with Tenor to drive social momentum using GIFs, creating sustained tune-in for its shows {narcosLink}, {dearwhitepeopleLink}, {masterofnoneLink}, {thecrownLink} and the upcoming Will Smith feature film, {brightLink}.","The perfect {first3Terms} Animated GIF for your conversation. Discover and Share the best GIFs on Tenor.":"The perfect {first3Terms} animated GIF for your conversation. Discover and share the best GIFs on Tenor.","The popular {titleFragment} GIFs everyone's sharing":"The popular {titleFragment} GIFs that everyone's sharing","The {emotionlGraphLink} maps 4 billion distinct search terms to the GIFs that say it best. As a Tenor content partner, we’ll integrate your GIFs into this powerful matching engine and surface your content in relevant search results -- making it easy for consumers to find, share and enjoy it.":"The {emotionlGraphLink} maps four billion distinct search terms to the GIFs that say it best. As a Tenor content partner, we’ll integrate your GIFs into this powerful matching engine and surface your content in relevant search results – making it easy for consumers to find, share and enjoy it.","There was an issue processing {processingErrorsNum} of your files.":"There was an issue processing {processingErrorsNum} of your files.","There was an issue uploading {uploadErrorsNum} of your files. Please edit your upload and try again.":"There was an issue uploading {uploadErrorsNum} of your files. Please edit your upload and try again.","There was an issue uploading {uploadErrorsNum} of your files. Please edit your uploads and try again.":"There was an issue uploading {uploadErrorsNum} of your files. Please edit your uploads and try again.","This number reflects how many times your asset has been copied or shared to other platforms.":"This number reflects how many times your asset has been copied or shared to other platforms.","This upload and its associated tags will not be uploaded.":"This upload and its associated tags will not be uploaded.","Today":"Today","Top movie studios, TV networks, game publishers, sports leagues and storytellers team with Tenor to drive mobile shares and views of their GIFs.":"Top movie studios, TV networks, game publishers, sports leagues and storytellers team with Tenor to drive mobile shares and views of their GIFs.","Trending Tenor Searches":"Trending Tenor searches","Trim":"Trim","Turkish":"Turkish","Turn GIFs Into Stickers":"Turn GIFs into stickers","URL Upload":"URL upload","URL to your website":"URL to your website","Ukrainian":"Ukrainian","Unfortunately, login with email and password for Tenor has been deprecated. Tenor users were sent a notice back in 2022 to link their profile to a Google Account before January 1st, 2023":"Unfortunately, login with email address and password for Tenor has been deprecated. Tenor users were sent a notice back in 2022 to link their profile to a Google Account before 1 January 2023","Unity AR SDK":"Unity AR SDK","Unknown Error. Upload failed.":"Unknown error. Upload failed.","Unknown Error: Please try again.":"Unknown error: Please try again.","Up to {maxUploads} GIFs, MP4s, PNGs, JPGs":"Up to {maxUploads} GIFs, MP4s, PNGs, JPGs","Upload":"Upload","Upload GIFs and you’ll get notifications when people share or favorite them":"Upload GIFs and you’ll get notifications when people share or favourite them","Upload GIFs, and you’ll get notifications when people share or favorite them":"Upload GIFs, and you’ll get notifications when people share or favourite them","Upload Icon":"Upload icon","Upload To Tenor":"Upload to Tenor","Upload and Create":"Upload and create","Upload and edit your GIFs, stickers, or short MP4s to your Tenor profile to share with friends and family":"Upload and edit your GIFs, stickers or short MP4s to your Tenor profile to share with friends and family","Upload animated GIFs to Tenor to share on social media channels, text messages, and everywhere else.":"Upload animated GIFs to Tenor to share on social media channels, text messages and everywhere else.","Upload icon":"Upload icon","Upload your favorite GIFs!":"Upload your favourite GIFs!","Upload your own GIFs":"Upload your own GIFs","Uploader":"Uploader","Uploading...":"Uploading…","Urdu":"Urdu","Use of Tenor on LG is subject to the {link}":"Use of Tenor on LG is subject to the {link}","Username":"Username","Uzbek":"Uzbek","Vietnamese":"Vietnamese","View Favorites":"View Favourites","View Uploads":"View uploads","We could not find the page you were looking for.":"We could not find the page that you were looking for.","We make it easy to find and share the right GIF across devices. Tenor is the #1 downloaded and used GIF-sharing app on both iOS and Android.":"We make it easy to find and share the right GIF across devices. Tenor is the No.1 downloaded and used GIF-sharing app on both iOS and Android.","We've updated our {linkElements}. By continuing you agree to Tenor's {linkElements}.":"We've updated our {linkElements}. By continuing you agree to Tenor's {linkElements}.","Website Licenses":"Website licences","Welcome back!":"Welcome back!","Width":"Width","With Tenor, maker of GIF Keyboard, add popular {titleFragment} animated GIFs to your conversations. Share the best GIFs now \u003E\u003E\u003E":"With Tenor, maker of GIF keyboard, add popular {titleFragment} animated GIFs to your conversations. Share the best GIFs now \u003E\u003E\u003E","X axis":"X-axis","Y axis":"Y-axis","Yes":"Yes","Yesterday":"Yesterday","You do not have access to this page.":"You do not have access to this page.","You have selected {lang}":"You have selected {lang}","Your session has expired. Please log in.":"Your session has expired. Please log in.","Zulu":"Zulu","failed to load gif frames":"failed to load GIF frames","flag icon":"flag icon","here":"here","monthly users":"monthly users","searches every month":"searches every month","to upload to Tenor":"to upload to Tenor","trash icon":"Bin icon","unsupported data type {mediaType}":"unsupported data type {mediaType}","upload your media files by dropping them here":"upload your media files by dropping them here","view profile":"view profile","{countStr} share":"{countStr} share","{countStr} shares":"{countStr} shares","{filetypeErrorsNum} of your uploads could not be processed since it is not a GIF, MP4, PNG or JPEG":"{filetypeErrorsNum} of your uploads could not be processed since it is not a GIF, MP4, PNG or JPEG","{filetypeErrorsNum} of your uploads could not be processed since they are not GIFs, MP4s, PNGs, or JPEGs":"{filetypeErrorsNum} of your uploads could not be processed since they are not GIFs, MP4s, PNGs or JPEGs","{gifKeyboardLogo} for iMessage":"{gifKeyboardLogo} for iMessage","{h1_title} - {first3Terms} - Discover & Share GIFs":"{h1_title} – {first3Terms} – discover and share GIFs","{name} icon":"{name} icon","{statusCode} Error":"{statusCode} error","{titleFragment} GIF Pack":"{titleFragment} GIF pack","{titleFragment} GIFs":"{titleFragment} GIFs","{titleFragment} GIFs | Tenor":"{titleFragment} GIFs | Tenor","{trimmedTime}\u002F{trimmedLength} seconds":"{trimmedTime}\u002F{trimmedLength} seconds","{username} hasn’t uploaded any GIFs!":"{username} hasn’t uploaded any GIFs!","{username}'s GIFs on Tenor":"{username}'s GIFs on Tenor"},"url path component":{"about-faq":"about-faq","about-us":"about-us","collections":"collections","contact":"contact","contentpartners":"contentpartners","emotional-graph":"emotional-graph","explore":"explore","gif-maker":"gif-maker","imessage":"imessage","legacy-account-recover":"legacy-account-recover","legal-privacy":"legal-privacy","legal-privacy-update":"legal-privacy-update","legal-terms":"legal-terms","legal-terms-developer-update":"legal-terms-developer-update","legal-terms-update":"legal-terms-update","legal\u002Fdata-usage":"legal\u002Fdata-usage","legal\u002Fprivacy":"legal\u002Fprivacy","official":"official","packs":"packs","partners":"partners","press":"press","reactions":"reactions","search":"search","users":"users","view":"view"}},"tos":"\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Ca id=\"_folro4uvmxoj\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fa\u003ELast updated: 3 March 2021\u003C\u002Fh3\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETenor includes the Tenor mobile app, Tenor’s website (located at http:\u002F\u002Ftenor.com), the Tenor extensions and the Tenor API. The Tenor API may be integrated with third-party devices or services, but any Tenor-related services are provided by Google.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETo use Tenor, you must accept (1) the \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpolicies.google.com\u002Fterms?hl=en\"\u003EGoogle Terms of Service\u003C\u002Fa\u003E and (2) these Tenor Additional Terms of Service (the '\u003Cstrong\u003ETenor Additional Terms\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E').\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPlease read each of these documents carefully. Together, these documents are known as the '\u003Cstrong\u003ETerms\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E'. They establish what you can expect from us as you use our services, and what we expect from you.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIf these Tenor Additional Terms conflict with the \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpolicies.google.com\u002Fterms?hl=en\"\u003EGoogle Terms of Service\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, these Additional Terms will govern for Tenor.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAlthough it’s not a part of these Terms, we encourage you to read our \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpolicies.google.com\u002Fprivacy?hl=en\"\u003EPrivacy Policy\u003C\u002Fa\u003E to better understand how you can \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Faccount.google.com\u002F\"\u003Eupdate, manage, export and delete your information\u003C\u002Fa\u003E.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E1. Your content.\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETenor allows you to submit, store, send, receive or share your content. Your content is licensed to Google as described in the Google Terms of Service – so if you upload content to Tenor, we may display that content to users and share it when directed, and those users (including users who access content through the Tenor API) may view, share and modify that content.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E2. Prohibited content.\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003E2.1 You must not use Tenor for any commercial purpose or for the benefit of any third party.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003E2.2 As we explain in the Google Terms of Service, we want to maintain a respectful environment for everyone. When using Tenor, you must follow our \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fsupport.google.com\u002Ftenor\"\u003EProgramme policies\u003C\u002Fa\u003E and the basic rules of conduct described in the Google Terms of Services. In particular, when using Tenor, you must not:\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ea. submit, store, send or share any content that:\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ei. violates, or encourages any conduct that would violate, applicable law or others' rights, including any content that infringes, misappropriates or violates someone else's intellectual property rights, or rights of publicity or privacy;\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eii. contains personal or contact information about any other person without their prior authorisation;\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eiii. promotes illegal or harmful activities or substances;\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eiv. is fraudulent, misleading or deceptive;\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ev. is false or defamatory;\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Evi. is obscene or pornographic;\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Evii. promotes or constitutes discrimination, bigotry, racism, hatred, harassment or harm against any individual or group;\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eviii. is violent or threatening or promotes violence or actions that are threatening to any individual, group or organisation; or\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eb. send any unsolicited or unauthorised advertising, promotional materials or communications, including email, mail, spam, chain letters or other solicitations.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003E2.3 Any content assessed as inappropriate, illegal or incompatible may be restricted or removed. We use a combination of systems to identify and assess content generated by or uploaded into our services that violates our policies, such as these terms, Google \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpolicies.google.com\u002Fterms\"\u003ETerms of Service\u003C\u002Fa\u003E, or that violates the law. However, we understand that we sometimes make mistakes. If you think that your content doesn't violate these terms or was removed in error, you can appeal.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou may be restricted from using our service, or have your account suspended or terminated if:\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003Eyou materially or repeatedly breach these terms;\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003Ewe're required to do so to comply with a legal requirement or a court order;\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003Cli\u003Ewe reasonably believe that your conduct causes harm or liability to a user, a third-party or Tenor – for example, by hacking, phishing, harassing, spamming, misleading others or scraping content that doesn't belong to you or you have submitted, stored, shared or sent any prohibited content.\u003C\u002Fli\u003E\u003C\u002Ful\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFor more information about why we disable accounts and what happens when we do, see this Help Centre \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fsupport.google.com\u002Faccounts\u002Fanswer\u002F40695?sjid=7465486218302094232-NA\"\u003Earticle\u003C\u002Fa\u003E. If you believe that your Tenor Account has been suspended or terminated in error, you can \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fsupport.google.com\u002Faccounts\u002Fanswer\u002F40695?sjid=7465486218302094232-NA\"\u003Eappeal\u003C\u002Fa\u003E.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E"}</script></body></html>